rComments: He is a really creative prof. He has his own way to teach. It a bit of heavy coursework for me. However, if you follow his request you will receive a really good mark!

Dr. Strangelove is a down-to-earth prof who cares about his students and engages in very thought out and inspiring lectures. You get out of this class what you put in - as he says... and it is very true. The assignments are quite easy and take 10 minutes to 2 hours each week. 100% recommend having him as a prof.
Very good lecturer. Clear and elaborate, doesn't go too fast, has the perfect amount on slides. Makes class fun!
